---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const updated = 'June 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms & Conditions"
  description="The terms for using Life Momentum Score — a free productivity and self-improvement tool. Plain, simple, and no surprises."
>
  <article class="container-page py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-mute">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-body">
        By using Life Momentum Score, you agree to the terms below. We've kept them short and
        readable on purpose.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-10">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">What this is</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            Life Momentum Score is a free productivity and self-improvement tool that helps you
            track positive and negative habits and see the net direction of your behavior over
            time. It is intended for personal reflection and habit awareness.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">No guarantees of results</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            The tool can help you notice patterns, but it cannot do the work for you. We make no
            promises or guarantees about any specific outcome, improvement, or result you may or may
            not achieve from using it.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Your decisions are your own</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            You are responsible for your own choices, decisions, and actions. Life Momentum Score is
            not a substitute for professional medical, psychological, financial, or other expert
            advice. Use your own judgment, and consult a qualified professional where appropriate.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">The service may evolve</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            We may add, change, or remove features over time as the product develops. We may also
            update these terms; when we do, we'll revise the date above. Continuing to use the tool
            after a change means you accept the updated terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Provided “as is”</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            Life Momentum Score is provided as is, without warranties of any kind, whether express
            or implied. To the fullest extent permitted by law, we are not liable for any loss or
            damage arising from your use of the tool. Since your data is stored locally in your
            browser, keeping your own backups is your responsibility.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Questions</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-body">
            If you have any questions about these terms, you can reach us through
            <a href="/contact" class="text-ink underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-ink">our contact page</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary inline-flex">Start Tracking</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="btn btn-secondary inline-flex">Read the Privacy Policy</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
